{"tid":748242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本人到底點睇邪教","createTime":"2018-07-19T05:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T11:40:53.000Z","uid":90413,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"46e9254bc07864d99cb74bbad0ec31735baa5b9f","tid":748242,"uid":90413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T05:10:01.000Z","msg":"先唔講信既人 壓力大到 心靈脆弱到比人入侵<br />\n唔信既人又會點睇<br />\n<br />\n最近日本咁多天災 我覺得邪教應該又會做野<br />\n又有藉口發大黎搞 對呢啲玩弄人心既野好唔明白<br />\n雖然當局者迷 但係要幾冇信念 心理差先會中招<br />\n不過日本人奴性 同埋邪教勢力都大啲<br />\n<br />\n韓國唔駛講 直頭完全深入國家咁<br />\n好似最高層係邪教控制咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef7bd2e995f815f182516ab14b033dbb8dc6cd6","tid":748242,"uid":109050,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T05:10:51.000Z","msg":"難為正邪定分界"},{"pid":"25358b0be777981f1eb8bfcf4bb3b3d8336565b2","tid":748242,"uid":179547,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T05:11:58.000Z","msg":"殊樂咇咇"},{"pid":"cb00626328eaf53190d6c92b96a898fc07e9a282","tid":748242,"uid":71913,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"25358b0be777981f1eb8bfcf4bb3b3d8336565b2","tid":748242,"uid":179547,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T05:11:58.000Z","msg":"殊樂咇咇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T05:29:27.000Z","msg":"南無超"},{"pid":"84b0211afde5cbeb744d15ee9f6ecaf23b265acb","tid":748242,"uid":90413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T09:38:56.000Z","msg":"有冇住日本既朋友解答到？"},{"pid":"6dd2e6458d0c2e8c3e9996fb560b826babc320f4","tid":748242,"uid":190749,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T09:39:38.000Z","msg":"用眼睇"},{"pid":"eeb52d1ced72a75d36274e1f2e001294ae647b7c","tid":748242,"uid":64290,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T09:58:15.000Z","msg":"點解係child登問?"},{"pid":"073727dffd911cec6251d377cc7a0fb68a99a074","tid":748242,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018